sentences: Tamer Karadağlı (born 24 May 1967) is a Turkish actor.
In 1993 he made his television debut in Ferhunde Hanımlar .
In 2012, he starred with Seda Eğridere in the Turkish action film Alina, the Turkish Assassin.
He married the actress Arzu Balkan in 2002 but they divorced in 2007.
